Stephen MARKGRAF, petitioner,
v.
A.D., a Minor, et al. No. 13-365. Supreme Court of the United States Nov. 4, 2013.

Case below, 712 F.3d 446.

Motion of California State Association of Counties for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit denied.
